post.description: Approves and launches the server component update.

Tests whether all relations between the specified item and other items form the same folder can be removed. I.e. if the item can be completely unlinked from the specified other items. This method takes into account module permissions, columns permissions, workflow actions effects and eWay-CRM end user business logic. That is why it can respond that relation cannot be removed even though you technically have the permission to remove the relations.
